      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready for a dependable ride that's full of character! This vehicle is in honest, fair condition and is the perfect choice for someone looking for a reliable daily driver at a fantastic price. While it shows some signs of its journey so far, it has plenty of life left and is ready to hit the road with its next owner today!",
