    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an automotive specimen of unparalleled caliber. This vehicle remains in concours-level condition, reflecting a standard of preservation rarely encountered in the pre-owned market. Every surface, from the flawless exterior finish to the pristine interior appointments, adheres to original factory specifications. Meticulously maintained and rigorously inspected, this unit offers the discerning collector or enthusiast an opportunity to acquire a vehicle that transcends the typical secondary market offering. We invite serious inquiries to appreciate this benchmark of excellence.",
